    "title": "small initial dialog size in transactiondescdialog.ui",
    "body": "When in HiDPI settings, transactiondescdialog is too small initially, though it is re-sizable. \nthe reason is that it uses hard-coded size in .ui file. hard-coded to have size\n\n```\n<width>620</width>\n<height>250</height>\n```\n\nThat's problematic on platform that don't use pixel ratio, but just pre-monitor DPI settings, like windows >= 8  and Linux.\n\ninitial size should be set by  overloadding sizeHint() and use this->fontMetrics() to calculate a proper size.\n",
